thread.title: Justin

author: Justin
title: Justin
text: I am an occasional user of phenibut for anxiety and insomnia purposes and I've tried other companies and none of them have ever compared to the pure quality of phenibut from liftmode and I will never waste my money with another company again. It's also a great price and the service is excellent. I'd recommend to anyone that they can order with 100% confidence that they are getting the best.
